        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Half-dragons are only rarely the result of dragons mating with other creatures\u2014most are the result of strange magical experiments. In most cases, a successful creation breeds true with others of its kind, as with the dreaded dracolisk."
        }
